## [1] 32563.99

\[\pi(\theta|x)=32564\theta^5(1-\theta)^{15} \]

theta <- seq(0.1,0.9,0.1)
post <- 32564*theta^5*(1-theta)^15
plot(post)

level <- 0.95

post.sort=sort(post,decreasing = T)
M=min(which(cumsum(post.sort)>=level))
height=post.sort[M]
HPD.index=which(post>=height)
HPD.level=sum(post[HPD.index])
HPD=list(index=HPD.index, level=HPD.level)

#최대사후구간
c(min(theta[HPD$index]),max(theta[HPD$index]))
## [1] 0.1 0.4
